---
title: Carb Smart Chicken Fajita Plates with Chive Crema and Sweet Potato Rounds
description: This free-form fajita plate swaps traditional tortilla wraps for roasted sweet potato rounds, delivering layers of warming, toasty flavour with the same satisfaction!

